{"tid":1217922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有錄音)啱啱收到葵涌醫院電話，懷疑有女院友喊住留言，好詭異","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:24:34.000Z","uid":19439,"like":642,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":141,"replies":[{"pid":"02aee8c65f22cfe1c839088a01f726527562c627","tid":1217922,"uid":19439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱收到個2字頭電話無聽，上網check返，應該係葵涌醫院打黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH0Mfun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH0Mfun.jpg&h=10173592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵涌醫院（英語：Kwai Chung Hospital，醫院管理局內部代碼：KCH）是香港醫院管理局轄下的一所<strong><strong>精神科醫院</strong></strong>，位於新界葵青區下葵涌荔景，毗鄰瑪嘉烈醫院；於1981年10月15日啟用，為九龍半島和新界西大部份地區的精神病病人提供評估、治療與住院服務。<br />\n<br />\n然後仲要有留言，即刻聽下係講啲咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://instaud.io/3Oba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstaud.io%2F3Oba&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=4518170f\" target=\"_blank\">https://instaud.io/3Oba</a><br />\n<br />\n聽到有把女仔聲喊住咁講野，背景聲有疑似職員講野<br />\n成段錄音好模，唔知各位巴絲聽唔聽得清楚，成件事好詭異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7915682f929e4131044c78ed8a47d5fd750259f0","tid":1217922,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3320f96fa3c9c1a90daeff5462046d5b585b0f4a","tid":1217922,"uid":19439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de6143aacc29c65b21ca03a20d9fb8b38ed3fda4","tid":1217922,"uid":76366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bf72f383e894e7463351dbfe085a29bcd074069","tid":1217922,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"494d8efbf458c295591e3db636e39145640abb12","tid